Contents of app subdirectory
----------------------------
SHERMAN1                 - test matrix
bpfort.h                 - include file for fortran interface
makefile                 - makefile for different architectures
equiv                    - additional compiler options on CRAY

simple.cc                - simple C++ test example
f1example.f              - fortran example 1
f2example.f              - fortran example 2
f3example.f              - fortran example 3
c_example.c              - C example
B22.cc B22.h b22_test.cc - files for b22_test
bp.cc                    - testbed application

partit                   - partitioning file input to bp
test_script              - test script
test_output              - test output
